StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetStagingImportPersonListByStatus]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ImportEventId uniqueiden..er, @StatusTypeId int
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT ImportPersonStagingID, ImportEventID, ImportStatusID, ChildEventID, FirstName, MiddleName, LastName, Street, City, State, Zip, Phone, Gender, Email FROM [PROSPECTING].[UPLOAD].[ImportPersonStaging] WHERE ImportEventId=@ImportEventId AND ImportStatusId=@StatusTypeId
END
